    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><style>[data-colorid=jbk6j1w90w]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jbk6j1w90w]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=uytm96p69o]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=uytm96p69o]{color:#004eb3}</style><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Elio_lighting.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/Elio_lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761238687390&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=318\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/399245378/Elio_lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761238687390&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"402\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"630980770\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Elio_lighting.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"399245378\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"15\" data-media-id=\"06c3202f-1aef-4011-93e2-572839f5e503\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/Elio_lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761238687390&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=636 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/Elio_lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761238687390&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=318 1x\" /></span><p>RenderMan ships with a full set of analytic and photorealistic lights.  </p><p>This quick guide below aims to help you determine which light to use for what lighting purpose.</p><p /><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"06d1762d-0396-4c66-8318-ae31546758a5\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 186.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 573.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"uytm96p69o\">RenderMan Light</span></strong></p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"jbk6j1w90w\">Uses</span></strong></p></th></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"PxrDomeLight.svg\" width=\"51\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrDomeLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242574182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/399245378/PxrDomeLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242574182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"32\" data-width=\"32\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"630915289\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDomeLight.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"399245378\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"15\" data-media-id=\"45e5f8fe-e8c8-4547-b84e-56d09a0e6d73\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrDomeLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242574182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrDomeLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242574182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 1x\" /></span><p><strong>PxrDomeLight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p /><p>In much visual effects and animation work, scenes are lit primarily using a High Dynamic Range Image (HDRI) or a hand-painted sky ramp texture.</p><p>They can also be used to add a rim light to a character, as they provide a nice, even rim-lighting effect.</p><p /></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrRectLight.svg\" width=\"49\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrRectLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242665972&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/399245378/PxrRectLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242665972&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"32\" data-width=\"32\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"631308423\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrRectLight.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"399245378\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"15\" data-media-id=\"a8fb6b30-2005-43f6-95c9-e5af4415a32f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrRectLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242665972&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrRectLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242665972&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 1x\" /></span><p><strong>PxrRectLight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p /><p>A large rectangular light that mimics a photographic light panel or softbox.  </p><p>One of the most commonly used lights in rendering.  </p><p>For realistic reflections and light quality, apply a texture to the light.</p><p>A general light used in lighting for many looks and can also be used for adding interior fill light from a ceiling or wall.</p><p>This is also used to add bounce lighting from walls or bounce board geometry.</p><p /></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrDiskLight.svg\" width=\"51\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrDiskLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242702850&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/399245378/PxrDiskLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242702850&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"32\" data-width=\"32\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"631210133\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDiskLight.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"399245378\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"15\" data-media-id=\"5eab4dab-bf6a-4728-9618-cf8e24e97813\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrDiskLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242702850&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrDiskLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242702850&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 1x\" /></span><p><strong>PxrDiscLight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p /><p>Same as a PxrRectLight, just in a disc shape</p><p /></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrDistantLight.svg\" width=\"49\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrDistantLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242730860&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/399245378/PxrDistantLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242730860&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"32\" data-width=\"32\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"631472134\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDistantLight.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"399245378\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"15\" data-media-id=\"71f65cd0-e71b-453e-a4a3-31d8519a89e3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrDistantLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242730860&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrDistantLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242730860&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 1x\" /></span><p><strong>PxrDistantLight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p /><p>Mainly use this for mimicking sunlight, moonlight, or a very distant light source</p><p /></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrSphereLight.svg\" width=\"49\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrSphereLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242755534&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/399245378/PxrSphereLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242755534&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"32\" data-width=\"32\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"631504900\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrSphereLight.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"399245378\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"15\" data-media-id=\"1c1e26ee-ae7b-4949-94a1-3e38b9dace7b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrSphereLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242755534&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrSphereLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242755534&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 1x\" /></span><p><strong>PxrSphereLight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p /><p>Often used to replicate practical light sources that emit light 360 degrees, such as candles, headlights, and lightbulbs.</p><p /></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrCylinderLight.svg\" width=\"49\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrCylinderLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242780170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/399245378/PxrCylinderLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242780170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"32\" data-width=\"32\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"630915295\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrCylinderLight.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"399245378\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"15\" data-media-id=\"fc8acce4-2c55-491b-b7fa-a4704fc3f0dd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrCylinderLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242780170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrCylinderLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242780170&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 1x\" /></span><p><strong>PxrCylinderLight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p /><p>Great for interior tube lighting, neons, and light sabers!</p><p /></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrPortalLight.svg\" width=\"49\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrPortalLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242808477&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/399245378/PxrPortalLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242808477&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"32\" data-width=\"32\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"631242876\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrPortalLight.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"399245378\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"15\" data-media-id=\"3f088662-a991-4418-8e7f-6e39693a66d7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrPortalLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242808477&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrPortalLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242808477&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 1x\" /></span><p><strong>PxrPortalLight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p /><p>Windows!</p><p /></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrEnvDayLight.svg\" width=\"53\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrEnvDayLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242840918&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/399245378/PxrEnvDayLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242840918&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"32\" data-width=\"32\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"631177374\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrEnvDayLight.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"399245378\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"15\" data-media-id=\"4b21548b-e007-42c7-8377-20f928f69dcf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrEnvDayLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242840918&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/399245378/PxrEnvDayLight.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761242840918&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=32&amp;height=32 1x\" /></span><p><strong>PxrEnvDaylight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p /><p>Daylight simulations are helpful when you want a quick, easy setup for exterior lighting or maybe some look development time, but you don't have an HDRI for the PxrDomeLight. The simplicity and realism make this light a favorite for artists.</p><p /></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p />"
    }
